Sisonke 2 enrolled 227 310 HCW from the 8 November to the 17 December 2021. We estimated vaccine effectiveness (VE) of the Ad26.COV2.S vaccine booster in 69 092 HCW as compared to unvaccinated individuals enrolled in the same managed care organization using a test negative design.
